org.apache.jackrabbit.core.observation
Class ObservationManagerFactory

java.lang.Object
  org.apache.jackrabbit.core.observation.ObservationManagerFactory
All Implemented Interfaces:
EventDispatcher, Runnable
public final class ObservationManagerFactory
extends Object
implements EventDispatcher, Runnable

The class ObservationManagerFactory creates new ObservationManager instances for sessions. It also implements the EventDispatcher interface where EventStateCollections can be dispatched to EventListeners.
